title: Supervillain: the Making of Tekashi 6ix9ine
overview: Supervillain: the Making of Tekashi 6ix9ine profiling hip-hop artist Tekashi 6ix9ine's epic rise to notoriety. Through an exclusive interview with the incendiary rapper after his release from prison earlier this spring, director Karam Gill examines the culture of manufactured celebrity through 6ix9ine's mastery of social media.
